Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是黑巫女  椿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是前来阻挠咒术的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒老早就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的  我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难伺候的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们想借用一下那股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还很痛恨桔梗对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第60话 黑巫女 五十年的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个你念念看  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前学过的也忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像愈来愈被抛在后面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那个  旧男友的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个明明劈腿甩掉戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又爱吃醋的暴力任性男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是还牵扯不清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神嘛  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点忘了他比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛  那个臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他果然不想分手对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要干脆点分了才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…那个呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又回到原点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他也有温柔的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很平常嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么这么沮丧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我最近一直请假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课业有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  因为戈薇常常请假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算每天上课也有可能跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只要确实做好预习与复习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课就能很快乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么怎么怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了不好的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为步美一直很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是太晚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙又会跑来接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还会来接你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真的是很体贴的男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  他明明很爱吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们又和好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这样没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是致密的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧了  老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我来到底有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约五十年前  你应该还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾和叫做桔梗的巫女战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺取四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意为我所用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借给你力量  我能得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给你四魂之玉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的手上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆变的妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我本来的面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个女人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了永保青春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把魂魄出卖给妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对方还是不怎样的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人应该渴望更强的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你说有四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算用四魂之玉做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是永保青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你希望我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给七宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是犬夜叉喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别只顾着拿零嘴…拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样的也该带一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多各式各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御神酒和护身符也带去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不用了啦  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你已经要出发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有人在等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是犬夜叉哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想试着去战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你去了  因为你是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会想回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太年纪还太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐就不会怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概都已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就放着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有够久耶  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说太阳下山前就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说太阳下山前就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有感觉到什么吧  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有股奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是法师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…邪气悄悄的接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛在地面上爬一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?被咬了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  很慢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道被什么东西咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纸?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到那女人的血了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  再带我过去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很神气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我碰到一个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该算是解决掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没有被咬的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确有个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看那纸  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有带来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…式神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是…四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片变黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片  进入了我的身体里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入那女人体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会和充满奈落污秽的玉共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而侵蚀那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是心灵还是身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人的命运就任我摆布了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿  别小看那个叫戈薇的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫戈薇的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己中了诅咒都没发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为桔梗的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个多厉害的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你想怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样直接咒杀她也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让犬夜叉的恶梦再次重现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那与心爱的女人相互残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人怀念的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上之前的邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是某人在诅咒戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁敢诅咒戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是黑巫女的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在井边咬伤戈薇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是黑巫女的使魔  式神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该也知道她们的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门接受诅咒委托的邪恶巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片受到污染
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是那家伙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全进入戈薇的身体里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇或许会被碎片的毒毒死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出黑巫女然后打倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要断绝诅咒非这样做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留下来陪在戈薇身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个方向可以感受到邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上来  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了犬夜叉  杀了犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…别说了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还任性的抵抗着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫戈薇的女人\N是巫女桔梗的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的手段是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个半妖男人夺去了心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵力也衰弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取那家伙守护的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原本是最好的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人竟然把我放的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原封不动的打回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚  我不想取你性命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人故作清高的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来仍让我作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我去换个水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇还有救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…可能戈薇本身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在和诅咒战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇是很坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  再拖下去会承受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还束手无策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她垂死挣扎也差不多到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就实现你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒他们还没\N抵达黑巫女的所在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇明明这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然只能旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使身体被操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的心却还没丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这样更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿  如果犬夜叉逃离那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就不用客气  咒杀戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇一定是被黑巫女操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪气愈来愈强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经和它战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人我随时都能咒杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样让戈薇杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是逃走  让戈薇丧命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量痛苦吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
